description: The Chung County Museum preserves the remains and relics of Prime Minister Lee Won-ik and his direct descendants, the representative of the Joseon Dynasty. The exhibition hall (Chung Hyun Hall) displays various materials of the scholar-official family, such as relics and materials related to Lee Won-ik, and folk household items of the clan.
